**Benefits:**
- ‚úÖ Immediate protection if device compromised
- ‚úÖ User control over active sessions
- ‚úÖ Enhanced security for high-value accounts
- ‚úÖ Compliance with enterprise security requirements
- ‚úÖ Defense-in-depth security posture

**Limitations:**
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Only revokes refresh tokens (existing access tokens valid until expiration)
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Access tokens still valid for up to 1 hour after revocation
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Requires admin consent for Graph API permissions
